{"tid":2332281,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"交左app 裸聊勒索騙案新聞綜合post","createTime":"2020-12-19T13:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T04:51:37.000Z","uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e8b186ece052ceb86d036911079d51d755021930","tid":2332281,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T13:14:35.000Z","msg":"最新一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>秀茂坪14歲男童玩Line　遭人用不雅片勒索1.8萬元</strong><br />\n<br />\n今（19日）午3時許，秀茂坪秀明道一名14歲男童在社交應用程式Line，懷疑被人以一段不雅影片勒索1.8萬元，家人報警求助。警方初步調查後，將案件列作勒索，交由秀茂坪警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。"},{"pid":"1b164a6238ea115c9fc4d75bff29b9cc0bf2cd6e","tid":2332281,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T13:15:29.000Z","msg":"Heymandi<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今（11日）下午4時許，居住黃大仙慈雲山道一戶姓潘家人向警方報案，指家中一名17歲青年玩匿名交友app「<strong><span class=\"red\">Heymandi</span></strong> 」時，遭人拍下裸聊影片兼勒索2千元。警方經初步調查，案件列勒索，交由黃大仙警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。"},{"pid":"d0f0a31452d1297058e340728d60d75877247e9c","tid":2332281,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T13:17:01.000Z","msg":"14歲就有18000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2511115d5e7551f1801cdd49891c42531c63725d","tid":2332281,"uid":90660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T13:17:09.000Z","msg":"用條牙籤諗野<br />\n抵撚死"},{"pid":"7b39b5c10949e1afb8602e9b8e7ef8478e6fd8fb","tid":2332281,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2511115d5e7551f1801cdd49891c42531c63725d","tid":2332281,"uid":90660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T13:17:09.000Z","msg":"用條牙籤諗野<br />\n抵撚死"},"citedBy":